name: Raw video player
tagline: Raw video Player for Linux platform
body:
### Welcome to raw_video_player
From here, you can download the source-code as tar or zip file. Also you can check the code on the git-repository as well. To clone this code, follow this:

```
$ cd any_path_you_want
$ git clone https://github.com/aman2467/raw_video_player.git
```
